Maintainer: Marc-André Lemay <marc-andre.lemay.2@ulaval.ca>
Description: This package allows the selection of polymorphic markers useful in defining
    haplotypes for genes from SNP data. Included are functions used to parse genotypic
    data (VCF and hapmap files), basic tools for filtering SNP data, as well as high-level
    data visualization tools.
